Map development was started in early february of 2019 and got abandoned in a month.
Roxy at this time was the main mapper, MaKo just made a stage.

MaKo picked up the map again in january 2020.
Because Roxy does not have alot of time anymore for mapping and surfing in general, MaKo finished it himself.
